The Telegraph - Calcutta : Metro

On amp; Off

The man and the money

 Sure? Confident? Lock kiya jaye? After months of endless wait, Kaun Banega Crorepati finally returns to the small screen tonight at 9. Here rsquo;s a sneak preview

 No more bandhgalas, quizmaster- host Amitabh Bachchan will be seen in snazzy printed shirts and leather jackets, designed by Shantanu and Nikhil. The fabrics have been imported from Australia, Italy and France. STAR TV, the host channel, feels that the show will be bigger this time around with Bachchan on top of the game unlike last time when he was almost down and outTo come on Fridays, Saturdays and Sundays every week, KBC 2 is being used by STAR to boost their weekend programming. ?Placing new and popular shows before and after KBC, we are looking at holding the audiences for a couple of hours at a stretch,? says Samir Nair, COO of STAR India

 Saif Ali Khan and Preity Zinta will be the first celebrity guests in the second innings of the show. Slated to appear together in the new Yash Raj film, Salaam Namaste, the two will be part of the Rakhi special episode.

 Apart from the prize money doubling to Rs 2 crore, there is an extra lifeline ? Flip The Question. Here, contestants can have the question changed once between questions 6 and 15.

 The nine contestants who make it to the Fastest Finger First but not on the hot seat, get a chance to Play Along with the hot seat participant and win Rs 2 lakh. Will it be one of the three Calcuttans?

 The Har Seat Hot Seat section will see Bachchan asking a special question for all those watching from home. Rush in your answers before the episode ends to the MTNL/BSNL landline 1904 424 7827 followed by the right option (01 or 02 or 03 or 04) or SMS ?KBC? to 646 followed by the right option (01 or 02 or 03 or 04). The lucky winner, selected by the computer, will get Rs 2 lakh




